SELECT
prt1.dataareaid as DATAAREAID
,prt1.pdsrebateid as PDSREBATEID
,prt1.custaccount as CUSTACCOUNT
,prt1.custinvoicetransrefrecid as CUSTINVOICETRANSREFRECID
,prt1.currencycode as CURRENCYCODE
,prt1.defaultdimension as DEFAULTDIMENSION
,prt1.offsetdefaultdimension as OFFSETDEFAULTDIMENSION
,prt1.itemid as ITEMID
,prt1.ledgerdimension as LEDGERDIMENSION
,prt1.offsetledgerdimension as OFFSETLEDGERDIMENSION
,prt1.tammerchandisingeventid as TAMMERCHANDISINGEVENTID
,prt1.pdsrebatetype as PDSREBATETYPE
,prt1.pdsrebateamttype as PDSREBATEAMTTYPE
,prt1.pdspaymttype as PDSPAYMTTYPE
,prt1.pdsrebatestatus as PDSREBATESTATUS
,prt1.pdsprocessdate as PDSPROCESSDATE
,prt1.rebatecalcdate as REBATECALCDATE
,prt1.pdsstartingrebateamt as PDSSTARTINGREBATEAMT
,prt1.modifieddatetime as MODIFIEDDATETIME
,cit1.dataareaid as CUSTINVOICETRANS_DATAAREAID
,cit1.numbersequencegroup as CUSTINVOICETRANS_NUMBERSEQUENCEGROUP
,cit1.salesid as CUSTINVOICETRANS_SALESID
,cit1.invoicedate as CUSTINVOICETRANS_INVOICEDATE
,cit1.invoiceid as CUSTINVOICETRANS_INVOICEID
,cit1.modifieddatetime as CUSTINVOICETRANS_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,cij1.orderaccount as CUSTINVOICEJOUR_ORDERACCOUNT
,cij1.modifieddatetime as CUSTINVOICEJOUR_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,tme1.promotionid as TAMMERCHANDISINGEVENT_PROMOTIONID
,tme1.modifieddatetime as TAMMERCHANDISINGEVENT_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,tet1.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE1_ENUMVALUELABEL_PDSREBATEAMTTYPE
,tet2.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE2_ENUMVALUELABEL_PDSPAYMTTYPE
,tet3.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE3_ENUMVALUELABEL_PDSREBATESTATUS
,(SELECT MAX(LastUpdateDate) 
 FROM (VALUES (prt1.modifieddatetime),
  (isnull(cit1.modifieddatetime, '1950-01-01'))
  , (isnull(cij1.modifieddatetime, '1950-01-01'))
  , (isnull(tme1.modifieddatetime, '1950-01-01'))
 ) AS UpdateDate(LastUpdateDate)) AS LATEST_MODIFIEDDATETIME
FROM
dbo.PDSREBATETABLE prt1
left join dbo.CUSTINVOICETRANS cit1 on
	prt1.CUSTINVOICETRANSREFRECID = cit1.RECID
left join (select DATAAREAID, NUMBERSEQUENCEGROUP, SALESID, INVOICEDATE, INVOICEID
			, ORDERACCOUNT
			, MODIFIEDDATETIME
		from dbo.CUSTINVOICEJOUR cij10
		inner join (select RECID
					, row_number() over (partition by DATAAREAID, NUMBERSEQUENCEGROUP, SALESID, INVOICEDATE, INVOICEID order by MODIFIEDDATETIME desc) as ROW_NUM
				from dbo.CUSTINVOICEJOUR) cij11 on
			cij11.ROW_NUM = 1 and
			cij10.RECID = cij11.RECID) cij1 on
	cit1.DATAAREAID = cij1.DATAAREAID and
	cit1.NUMBERSEQUENCEGROUP = cij1.NUMBERSEQUENCEGROUP and
	cit1.SALESID = cij1.SALESID and
	cit1.INVOICEDATE = cij1.INVOICEDATE and
	cit1.INVOICEID = cij1.INVOICEID
left join dbo.TAMMERCHANDISINGEVENT tme1 on
	prt1.DATAAREAID = tme1.DATAAREAID and
	prt1.TAMMERCHANDISINGEVENTID = tme1.MERCHANDISINGEVENTID
left join (select ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE
			, max(ENUMVALUELABEL) as ENUMVALUELABEL
		from dbo.TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE
		where ENUMNAME = 'PdsRebateAmtType'
		group by ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE) tet1 on
	prt1.PDSREBATEAMTTYPE = tet1.ENUMVALUE
left join (select ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE
			, max(ENUMVALUELABEL) as ENUMVALUELABEL
		from dbo.TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE
		where ENUMNAME = 'PdsPaymtType'
		group by ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE) tet2 on
	prt1.PDSPAYMTTYPE = tet2.ENUMVALUE
left join (select ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE
			, max(ENUMVALUELABEL) as ENUMVALUELABEL
		from dbo.TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE
		where ENUMNAME = 'PdsRebateStatus'
		group by ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE) tet3 on
	prt1.PDSREBATESTATUS = tet3.ENUMVALUE WHERE (SELECT MAX(LastUpdateDate) 
 FROM (VALUES (prt1.modifieddatetime),
  (isnull(cit1.modifieddatetime, '1950-01-01'))
  , (isnull(cij1.modifieddatetime, '1950-01-01'))
  , (isnull(tme1.modifieddatetime, '1950-01-01'))
 ) AS UpdateDate(LastUpdateDate)) > '@{variables('v_prev_max_timestamp')}'

@concat('select
prt1.dataareaid as DATAAREAID
,prt1.pdsrebateid as PDSREBATEID
,prt1.custaccount as CUSTACCOUNT
,prt1.custinvoicetransrefrecid as CUSTINVOICETRANSREFRECID
,prt1.currencycode as CURRENCYCODE
,prt1.defaultdimension as DEFAULTDIMENSION
,prt1.offsetdefaultdimension as OFFSETDEFAULTDIMENSION
,prt1.itemid as ITEMID
,prt1.ledgerdimension as LEDGERDIMENSION
,prt1.offsetledgerdimension as OFFSETLEDGERDIMENSION
,prt1.tammerchandisingeventid as TAMMERCHANDISINGEVENTID
,prt1.pdsrebatetype as PDSREBATETYPE
,prt1.pdsrebateamttype as PDSREBATEAMTTYPE
,prt1.pdspaymttype as PDSPAYMTTYPE
,prt1.pdsrebatestatus as PDSREBATESTATUS
,prt1.pdsprocessdate as PDSPROCESSDATE
,prt1.rebatecalcdate as REBATECALCDATE
,prt1.pdsstartingrebateamt as PDSSTARTINGREBATEAMT
,prt1.modifieddatetime as MODIFIEDDATETIME
,cit1.dataareaid as CUSTINVOICETRANS_DATAAREAID
,cit1.numbersequencegroup as CUSTINVOICETRANS_NUMBERSEQUENCEGROUP
,cit1.salesid as CUSTINVOICETRANS_SALESID
,cit1.invoicedate as CUSTINVOICETRANS_INVOICEDATE
,cit1.invoiceid as CUSTINVOICETRANS_INVOICEID
,cit1.modifieddatetime as CUSTINVOICETRANS_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,cij1.orderaccount as CUSTINVOICEJOUR_ORDERACCOUNT
,cij1.modifieddatetime as CUSTINVOICEJOUR_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,tme1.promotionid as TAMMERCHANDISINGEVENT_PROMOTIONID
,tme1.modifieddatetime as TAMMERCHANDISINGEVENT_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,tet1.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE1_ENUMVALUELABEL_PDSREBATEAMTTYPE
,tet2.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE2_ENUMVALUELABEL_PDSPAYMTTYPE
,tet3.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE3_ENUMVALUELABEL_PDSREBATESTATUS
,(select max(lastupdatedate) 
 from (values (prt1.modifieddatetime),
  (isnull(cit1.modifieddatetime, ''1950-01-01''))
  , (isnull(cij1.modifieddatetime, ''1950-01-01''))
  , (isnull(tme1.modifieddatetime, ''1950-01-01''))
 ) as updatedate(lastupdatedate)) as LATEST_MODIFIEDDATETIME
from '
,pipeline().globalParameters.d365_dbName,'.','pdsrebatetable prt1
left join  '
,pipeline().globalParameters.d365_dbName,'.','custinvoicetrans cit1 on
	prt1.custinvoicetransrefrecid = cit1.recid
left join (select dataareaid, numbersequencegroup, salesid, invoicedate, invoiceid
			, orderaccount
			, modifieddatetime
		from  '
,pipeline().globalParameters.d365_dbName,'.','custinvoicejour cij10
		inner join (select recid
					, row_number() over (partition by dataareaid, numbersequencegroup, salesid, invoicedate, invoiceid order by modifieddatetime desc) as row_num
				from  '
,pipeline().globalParameters.d365_dbName,'.','custinvoicejour) cij11 on
			cij11.row_num = 1 and
			cij10.recid = cij11.recid) cij1 on
	cit1.dataareaid = cij1.dataareaid and
	cit1.numbersequencegroup = cij1.numbersequencegroup and
	cit1.salesid = cij1.salesid and
	cit1.invoicedate = cij1.invoicedate and
	cit1.invoiceid = cij1.invoiceid
left join  '
,pipeline().globalParameters.d365_dbName,'.','tammerchandisingevent tme1 on
	prt1.dataareaid = tme1.dataareaid and
	prt1.tammerchandisingeventid = tme1.merchandisingeventid
left join (select enumname, enumvalue
			, max(enumvaluelabel) as enumvaluelabel
		from  '
,pipeline().globalParameters.d365_dbName,'.','timextenderenumtable
		where enumname = ''pdsrebateamttype''
		group by enumname, enumvalue) tet1 on
	prt1.pdsrebateamttype = tet1.enumvalue
left join (select enumname, enumvalue
			, max(enumvaluelabel) as enumvaluelabel
		from  '
,pipeline().globalParameters.d365_dbName,'.','timextenderenumtable
		where enumname = ''pdspaymttype''
		group by enumname, enumvalue) tet2 on
	prt1.pdspaymttype = tet2.enumvalue
left join (select enumname, enumvalue
			, max(enumvaluelabel) as enumvaluelabel
		from  '
,pipeline().globalParameters.d365_dbName,'.','timextenderenumtable
		where enumname = ''pdsrebatestatus''
		group by enumname, enumvalue) tet3 on
	prt1.pdsrebatestatus = tet3.enumvalue where (select max(lastupdatedate) 
 from (values (prt1.modifieddatetime),
  (isnull(cit1.modifieddatetime, ''1950-01-01''))
  , (isnull(cij1.modifieddatetime, ''1950-01-01''))
  , (isnull(tme1.modifieddatetime, ''1950-01-01''))
 ) as updatedate(lastupdatedate)) > ','''',variables('v_prev_max_timestamp'),'''')
